FBIS4-61111 "drsov086_a_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-086 Daily Report 4 May 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Border Guard Killed on Tajik-Afghan Border Border Guard Killed on Tajik-Afghan Border LD0405044894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0400 GMT 4 May 94 LD0405044894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Another Russian border guard has perished on the Tajik-Afghan border. According to a report from the Postfaktum agency, the guard was fatally wounded when the (Navrang) post in the sector of the 12th outpost of the Moskovskiy border guard detachment was fired on.
